{"tid":1132740,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"［法律求救］長命契轉左分權共有可否逆轉？？","createTime":"2019-04-30T13:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T13:09:53.000Z","uid":194789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"347347e371214befbf7d9be925850410fc0d3674","tid":1132740,"uid":194789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T13:48:35.000Z","msg":"本人同家母原本聯名共有一個單位（即長命契）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊同住左近30年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但因為家母年事已高就快80歲<br />\n老人家開始無咁精靈<br />\n<br />\n今日傾傾下計<br />\n發現佢比某親戚帶到律師樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不清不楚嘅情況下簽左做分權共有（拆契）<br />\n並除去左我個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n家母現家 患上左腦退化症<br />\n如果情況一直係咁<br />\n到佢離開果時 我就會無屋住 仲益埋個親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我可以點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望連登有人幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5444bf25c6ff5027c9f54dc112a340279dbae036","tid":1132740,"uid":103315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T13:51:23.000Z","msg":"左腦退化症=簽契時精神狀態有問題 有得challenge"},{"pid":"0b3b796f9876ca5d86a53af35ab0db0c2f49714f","tid":1132740,"uid":103315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T13:51:52.000Z","msg":"HCA 2390/2012"},{"pid":"565d276324152db520ac8c378d59125670ba96c7","tid":1132740,"uid":35965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":